column3: “This strain gets back to the basics in all the right ways. Its nostalgic aroma brings you back to simpler days, before hybrids and hyper strains. The high hits fast and hard, and youll find yourself surprised at how quickly this little blue flower takes you over the top. Once youre there, get ready to get stuff done, because you will be blasted with energy. This is my new favorite strain!!! Especially when i ne3d to ...”
